ğŸ“¸â€Research: We looked into the effects of increased salinity, due to sea level rise, in freshwater ecosystems. Specifically, we wanted to see how nitrogen, phosphorus, carbon and chlorophyll a (algae indicator) were affected by an increase of salt in the water.â€ -Eva Ascencio ğŸ’§ ğŸ
